{"tid":357337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"溫哥華回港航班，操華語夫婦被趕落機","createTime":"2017-08-12T18:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T15:45:51.000Z","uid":121079,"like":214,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e41aa34cffba08de02461d793d7539f7f888a6aa","tid":357337,"uid":121079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T18:00:52.000Z","msg":"時間：Aug 11, 2017<br />\n航班：AC007<br />\n<br />\n一對操捲脷口音華語夫婦，宣稱患病，<br />\n要求一個専用洗手間，或升級他們至商務客位。<br />\n該對夫妻另向機組人員要求註機醫生，<br />\n説機組人員需要提供保障給他倆。<br />\n<br />\n擾攘個多小時後，<br />\n機組人員為保障機上400多人之安全，<br />\n要求該對夫婦馬上離開航機，<br />\n叧需要得取醫生證明，<br />\n才能乘搭次日航班。<br />\n<br />\n該對夫婦眼見要求被佢絶，<br />\n同時又被要求離開航機，<br />\n馬上致電航空公司理論，<br />\n表現技巧熟練，<br />\n但最後仍難逃被趕落機的命運。<br />\n<br />\n利申：網上轉載，非親身經歷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/020027_aed274fd2afec02b7ae78de4b926ee19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F020027_aed274fd2afec02b7ae78de4b926ee19.jpg&h=c9a50d07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/020029_a1c10a5deb065a4671f86c3c6bad90a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F020029_a1c10a5deb065a4671f86c3c6bad90a1.jpg&h=eefe96d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/13/020031_1b797c06813806b21233b2bb3db08fb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F13%2F020031_1b797c06813806b21233b2bb3db08fb2.jpg&h=8ed0917d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2f892581169f7aa7985e88e933ce701a5f93a45","tid":357337,"uid":71257,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T18:08:42.000Z","msg":"有咁特殊嘅要求就應該上機之前幾日同航空公司講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cb3db604e8675e21e74c4c09f41b51da776055","tid":357337,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT